<div id="attachment_5346" style="width: 961px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2020/04/RJD_04_01_0012_0001_017.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-5346" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2020/04/RJD_04_01_0012_0001_017.jpg" alt="Mayor-elect Richard J. Daley stands with his family and supporters on election night, 1955" width="951" height="778" srcset="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2020/04/RJD_04_01_0012_0001_017.jpg 951w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2020/04/RJD_04_01_0012_0001_017-300x245.jpg 300w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2020/04/RJD_04_01_0012_0001_017-768x628.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 951px) 100vw, 951px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Mayor-elect Richard J. Daley stands with his family and supporters on election night, 1955. University of Illinois at Chicago Library, RJD_04_01_0012_0001_017.</p></div>
