			<article id="post-5306" class="et_pb_post clearfix et_pb_no_thumb post-5306 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-news-and-research-funds">

			
												<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/richard-m-daley-wins-democratic-party-nomination-for-cook-county-states-attorney/">Richard M. Daley wins Democratic Party nomination for Cook County State&#8217;s Attorney</a></h2>
				
				<p class="post-meta">  <span class="published">Mar 18, 2020</span>    </p><div class="post-content"><p>Forty years ago today, March 18, 1980, Richard M. Daley won the Democratic Party&#8217; nomination for Cook County State&#8217;s Attorney. Daley had been serving as a senator in the Illinois legislature since 1973, and before that, he had served in the Illinois state constitutional convention, or &#8220;Con Con.&#8221;</p>
<div id="attachment_5315" style="width: 2560px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2020/02/Temp_RMD16_06_0002_0001_013.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-5315" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2020/02/Temp_RMD16_06_0002_0001_013.jpg" alt="A flyer promotes Richard M. Daley for the position of Cook County State's Attorney, 1980" width="2550" height="3300" srcset="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2020/02/Temp_RMD16_06_0002_0001_013.jpg 2550w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2020/02/Temp_RMD16_06_0002_0001_013-232x300.jpg 232w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2020/02/Temp_RMD16_06_0002_0001_013-768x994.jpg 768w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2020/02/Temp_RMD16_06_0002_0001_013-791x1024.jpg 791w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2020/02/Temp_RMD16_06_0002_0001_013-1080x1398.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 2550px) 100vw, 2550px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">A flyer promotes Richard M. Daley for the position of Cook County State&#8217;s Attorney, 1980. Richard M. Daley papers, University of Illinois at Chicago Library, Temp_RMD16_06_0002_0001_013.</p></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</div>			
