				<p class="post-meta">  <span class="published">May 27, 2019</span>    </p><div class="post-content"><div id="attachment_4890" style="width: 773px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2019/05/MSLASZ13_0001_0004_003.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-4890" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2019/05/MSLASZ13_0001_0004_003.jpg" alt="Unidentified military man, West German Chancellor Willy Brandt, and Mayor Richard J. Daley at Eternal Flame in Civic Center Plaza, 1973" width="763" height="970" srcset="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2019/05/MSLASZ13_0001_0004_003.jpg 763w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2019/05/MSLASZ13_0001_0004_003-236x300.jpg 236w" sizes="(max-width: 763px) 100vw, 763px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Unidentified military man, West German Chancellor Willy Brandt, and Mayor Richard J. Daley at Eternal Flame in Civic Center Plaza, 1973. Photo: Laszlo Kondor. MSLASZ13_0001_0004_003</p></div>
