			<article id="post-4565" class="et_pb_post clearfix et_pb_no_thumb post-4565 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-news-and-research-funds">

			
												<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/chicago-mayor-richard-j-daley-visits-europe-1964/">Chicago Mayor Richard J. Daley visits Europe (1964)</a></h2>
				
				<p class="post-meta">  <span class="published">May 1, 2019</span>    </p><div class="post-content"><h2>Leaving for Europe</h2>
<p>Fifty-five years ago this month, in May 1964, Chicago Mayor Richard J. Daley and his wife, Eleanor &#8220;Sis&#8221; Daley, visited Europe. They accompanied other American politicians on parts of this visit, including Wisconsin Governor John Reynolds and Minnesota Governor Karl H. Rolvaag.Â They left for Copenhagen, Denmark on the inaugural Scandinavian Airlines direct flight from Chicago, arriving May 1.</p>
<div id="attachment_4739" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2019/03/RJD_04_01_0023_0005_001.jpg"><img class="size-medium wp-image-4739" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2019/03/RJD_04_01_0023_0005_001-300x243.jpg" alt="Inaugural SAS flight to Copenhagen and Ireland, Eleanor and Richard J. Daley and others, 1964" width="300" height="243" srcset="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2019/03/RJD_04_01_0023_0005_001-300x243.jpg 300w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2019/03/RJD_04_01_0023_0005_001-768x623.jpg 768w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2019/03/RJD_04_01_0023_0005_001.jpg 953w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Inaugural SAS flight to Copenhagen and Ireland, Eleanor and Richard J. Daley and others, 1964. Metro News Photo, RJD_04_01_0023_0005_001</p></div>
<h2>Itineraries</h2>
<div id="attachment_4738" style="width: 160px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2019/03/RJD_01_01_0049_0002_003.jpg"><img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-4738" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2019/03/RJD_01_01_0049_0002_003-150x150.jpg" alt="Itinerary for Europe trip, page 1., 1964" width="150" height="150" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Itinerary for Europe trip, page 1., 1964. RJD_01_01_0049_0002_003</p></div>
